  "instructions": [
    "Heat the olive oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the chopped onion and cook until translucent.",
    "Add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the diced nectarines and cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Add the uncooked white rice and stir to combine.",
    "Add the coconut milk, salt, and black pepper, and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce the heat to low, cover, and simmer for 18 minutes.",
    "Remove from heat and let sit for 5 minutes before serving."
